==Introduction==
優れた航続距離を誇り、初期の機動部隊艦載機の主力攻撃機として大活躍した傑作艦上攻撃機「九七艦攻」。<br>
同機を装備した本部隊は、高い技量と豊かな指導力を兼ね備えた村田隊長の率いる精鋭九七艦攻隊です。<br>

''Boasting an excellent cruising range, the "Type 97" was a masterpiece carrier-capable attack aircraft that played a major role as the primary attack aircraft on board Mobile Force ships.''<br>
''The command squadron equipped with this aircraft was the elite attack squadron led by Captain Murata, who combined high skill with abundant leadership.''

